"{\"uid\": \"cnbc.com-2024-09-17-tom-cruise-performed-paris-olympics-skydiving-stunt-for-free.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Related Stories  Tom Cruise is no stranger to big Hollywood paydays, but his latest role came free of charge.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 29, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 48, \"end\": 61, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breitbart_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"big Hollywood\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breitbart_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breitbart_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The actor stole the show during the closing ceremonies of the Paris Olympics, performing a stunt during the symbolic handoff to host-city-in-waiting Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 262, \"end\": 273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999883846418668, \"rank\": 1.1615480116998556e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking on a panel duringCNBC x Boardroom's Game Plan Summit,\\u00a0president of the Los Angles Olympic Organizing Committee Casey Wasserman said that getting the A-lister to participate was always his top priority, but he was skeptical of how much time he'd be able to get on Cruise's calendar.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 321, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Game_Plan_(TV_series)\", \"score\": 0.8044691971803887, \"rank\": 0.24305555555558886, \"text\": \"Game Plan\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Game_Plan_(TV_series)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Game_Plan_(TV_series)\"}, {\"begin\": 356, \"end\": 366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Los Angles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 396, \"end\": 411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Casey Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were like 'There is no way we are getting this much.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going to have four hours of filming time [with him].\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will do the thing in LA with the Hollywood sign, he will hand the thing off and he's done.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 721, \"end\": 735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rest will be just a stunt double,'\\\" Wasserman recalled.\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 819, \"end\": 828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"score\": 0.9999972552062826, \"rank\": 2.74407173259125e-06, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the 62-year-old Cruise quickly surprised the Organizing Committee with his enthusiasm and interest in their pitch.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"About five minutes into the presentation he goes 'I am in, but I am only doing it if I get to do everything,'\\\" Wasserman said.\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1072, \"end\": 1081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"score\": 0.9999972552062826, \"rank\": 2.74407173259125e-06, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wasserman said Cruise \\\"got more involved and engaged\\\" as planning for the closing ceremony stunt got underway.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1089, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"score\": 0.9999972552062826, \"rank\": 2.74407173259125e-06, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The stunt would see him rappel down from the roof of the Stade de France and accept the Olympic flag from Simone Biles and Los Angeles mayor Karen Bass.\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1307, \"end\": 1319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 1324, \"end\": 1335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999883846418668, \"rank\": 1.1615480116998556e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruise would then ride off on a motorcycle and the feed would cut to pre-taped footage of him riding onto a waiting plane which would fly him to Los Angeles, at which point he would skydive down onto the Hollywood sign.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1499, \"end\": 1510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999883846418668, \"rank\": 1.1615480116998556e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1558, \"end\": 1572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wasserman said Cruise was true to his word, arranging a jam-packed travel day in order to film everything that was needed.\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"score\": 0.9999972552062826, \"rank\": 2.74407173259125e-06, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He finished filming 'Mission: Impossible' at six o'clock in London, got right on a plane and landed in LA at 4 a.m.,\\\" Wasserman explained.\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1760, \"end\": 1766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999794987145988, \"rank\": 1.0796896267698358e-05, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1818, \"end\": 1827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"score\": 0.9999972552062826, \"rank\": 2.74407173259125e-06, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He filmed the scene where he pulls onto the military plane in LA.\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He did two jumps out of the plane.\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then he helicoptered from Palmdale to the Hollywood sign, filmed from one until five, helicoptered to the Burbank airport and flew back to London at six o'clock.\\\"\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1967, \"end\": 1975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palmdale_Transportation_Center\", \"score\": 0.9647489994990378, \"rank\": 0.036539038152581436, \"text\": \"Palmdale\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palmdale_Transportation_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palmdale_Transportation_Center\"}, {\"begin\": 1983, \"end\": 1997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}, {\"begin\": 2047, \"end\": 2062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Burbank_Airport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Burbank airport\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Burbank_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Burbank_Airport\"}, {\"begin\": 2080, \"end